title: Wings and Wheels at Dunsfold Aerodrome Surrey 29/30 August

posts.content:
Hi.
Is anyone planning on attending this?
I am going with the bus on Saturday 29th and have been accepted as a static exhibitor, so getting cheaper tickets.
They tell me i am the only bus so if anyone fancies it?
Its the Vulcans last year of flying and she flys both saturday and sunday around 1500 apparently. Those four jet engines actually make more noise than a vw - unbelievable!
Did you go on sat I saw a video of a green splitty doing the parade Saturday on get Surrey site. I went Sunday in my split there was one other there on Sunday in brooklands stand.
